 GROUP: 1
  NAME: CYCLOSPORIN A
  CHAIN: B, F, L, P, R
  COMPONENT_1: PEPTIDE LIKE SEQUENCE RESIDUES 1 TO 11
  DESCRIPTION: CYCLOSPORIN IS A CYCLIC UNDECAPEPTIDE.
